snippet.title: REAL MADRID 5 - 1 REAL BETIS | RESUMEN LALIGA EA SPORTS
snippet.description:
Goleada del Real Madrid por 5-1 ante el Real Betis en el Santiago Bernabéu, en un encuentro marcado por la gran actuación de Gonzalo, autor de un hat-trick. El delantero abrió el marcador de cabeza en la primera parte y amplió la ventaja tras el descanso con un potente disparo desde la frontal. Raúl Asencio firmó el tercer tanto a balón parado antes de que Cucho Hernández recortara distancias para el Betis. En el tramo final, Gonzalo completó su triplete y Fran García cerró el marcador en el tiempo añadido. 

#RealMadridRealBetis LALIGA EA SPORTS 2025/26 J18
Suscríbete al canal de LALIGA EA SPORTS: https://www.youtube.com/@LaLiga

snippet.title: FAST & FURIOUS 11 (2026) - First Trailer | Vin Diesel, Cristiano Ronaldo
snippet.description:
#FastAndFurious11 #VinDiesel #JasonMomoa #CristianoRonaldo

Editing, Adobe Premiere, VFX, SFX, Thumbnail by ‪‪@USTrailerStudio‬ please subscribe for more:

🎥 Attention Viewers!

This video is a fan-made cinematic concept, created for artistic expression and entertainment only. Powered by AI innovations (Google Veo 3), professional-grade sound design, and visual storytelling, it reimagines what modern filmmaking can be.
Every frame was built with creativity and passion—no official affiliation, just pure imagination.
Enjoy the experience, share the vision, and let’s keep pushing the boundaries of what’s possible in film. 🍿🎬

🚗 FAST & FURIOUS 11

Vin Diesel & Cody Walker vs Jason Momoa & Cristiano Ronaldo — The Battle of FAST & FURIOUS 11 (2026) delivers a powerful new chapter in the Fast Saga where family, legacy, and speed collide on the most dangerous battlefield yet — the frozen mountains of the Arctic. Dominic Toretto (Vin Diesel) and Brian O’Conner Jr. (Cody Walker) are forced into a high-stakes showdown against Dante Reyes (Jason Momoa) and Rafael “Veloce” Cruz (Cristiano Ronaldo), a ruthless driver bred for precision and victory. When Dante kidnaps Dom’s youngest son, the race becomes more than horsepower — it becomes survival. Each player starts by choosing an avatar and giving it an identity. They can then explore ROBLOX — interacting with others by chatting, playing games, or collaborating on creative projects. Each player is also given their own piece of undeveloped real estate along with a virtual toolbox with which to design and build anything — be it a navigable skyscraper, a working helicopter, a giant pinball machine, a multiplayer “Capture the Flag” game or some other, yet-to-be-dreamed-up creation. Watch Bloodsport 5 Fan Made Concept Trailer (2026)
The underground tournament returns and this time two legends must join forces to survive. This concept trailer reunites Jean-Claude Van Damme as Frank Dux alongside martial arts icon Jackie Chan in a battle that tests every bone in their bodies. When a dangerous new Kumite emerges with rules designed to break even the strongest fighters, old rivals become unlikely allies facing opponents who show no mercy. Fists fly, bones crack, and honor becomes the only currency that matters when stepping into a ring where walking out alive is never guaranteed.

What is Roblox? ROBLOX is an online virtual playground and workshop, where kids of all ages can safely interact, create, have fun, and learn. It’s unique in that practically everything on ROBLOX is designed and constructed by members of the community. ROBLOX is designed for 13 to 18 year olds, but it is open to people of all ages. Each player starts by choosing an avatar and giving it an identity. They can then explore ROBLOX — interacting with others by chatting, playing games, or collaborating on creative projects. Each player is also given their own piece of undeveloped real estate along with a virtual toolbox with which to design and build anything — be it a navigable skyscraper, a working helicopter, a giant pinball machine, a multiplayer “Capture the Flag” game or some other, yet-to-be-dreamed-up creation. There is no cost for this first plot of virtual land. By participating and by building cool stuff, ROBLOX members can earn specialty badges as well as ROBLOX dollars (“Robux”). In turn, they can shop the online catalog to purchase avatar clothing and accessories as well as premium building materials, interactive components, and working mechanisms.

snippet.title: ጫክ ጫካኮ||ዘማሪ ሞገስ አማኑኤል Caakki Caakakkoo New Song Moges Amanuel 2026
snippet.description:
ጫክ ጫካኮ ኡል ሁንዲና 2×.
ተንስ ጠኖዮ አመዴና 2×
  ሃሬች መን እንካሞ ኢየሱሳ ኤዴና
  ሁንድም መት አን ኦሶ ከኖ ሊራሞና
ኤ ቱንስ ዶሌ ህንጋሞ ጫከኔ ፍላሞ
ኢትኔ ዶሉካንና እልል ይኖሞ
    እልል ንዋዕና
    እልል ኢየሱስና 
    ፈዬናሞ ባጢዕል ጀብስ 2×
    ፍሉሞቴ ኬዕማል ቱንስ 2×
  
1) ባጢል ከራ ሄኑም ምናደባ 
     ብዕኖም ኡል ጢግኔ ሲዳ ኤባ 
     አድለኔካ ቄሶመኔካ 
     ኤዴሱኮ ኤ ኢመን ላከ
        ኮይ ሄኑም ኔሴ ኦስ እሳኮ
         ካዕሰም ኢታ ገትሳኮ 
        ሌህካ መላዬ እቃምሳኮ
        ሊራሞና ዶል ዋራኮ


2.እጥ  ኮሎ ሂንጭኔና ገዳኣ ሲንዳ
   አነናጥ ጎርተና ሌህኔ ግንዳ
  ሀዊክ አጠቂ ሀንሴ ድላ
  ሄሽኑም ዶሌ ጢግኔ ጉላ 
     መሶኦም ቤኤ መት አን ኦሶ
     ማሴአማ ጎጊ አን ቤዮ መሶ 
     ሃሬች መና ከባ ኔስ
     ሁንደም ሲዳኮ ኢየሱስ
     ሁንደም ሙጩሳ ኢየሱስ 

3)ዋዕ አድለን አናን እንካ
  ኡረቶ ሲንዶኔ ሄኑሞካ
  አነናቶ ቢዕሳ ለምቤዕካ
አረሱኮ ኢየሱስ ን ቤዮ ቢካ 
     ጡማ አለላታ መንሁንድና
     ጡፈማ ፎቃኣ እጦ ሞዕኖና
     እታንሳኮ ዋዕ ጌሬች 
     ኦኮ ፍራኮ ጡም ኤልንች
